        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In an effort to further fuse fashion and sports, J.Lindeberg has drawn inspiration from the Dominican Republic, specifically the luxurious Casa de Campo resort. This influence is evident in the rich hues and vibrant designs that permeate the collection. You'll find an array of pieces in coral, navy, turquoise, and white, each evoking the serene and picturesque landscapes of Hispaniola. These colours are not only visually appealing but also reflective of the tropical paradise that inspired them.</p>"
          }
        }
