    "text_6": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "A Closer Look at the Collection",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h5><strong>STATEMENT POLOS</strong></h5><p>Polos are a staple in any summer wardrobe, and J.Lindeberg offers a variety of options in their Summer 2024 collection. From statement print polos that make a bold impression to classic polos that exude understated elegance, there is something for everyone. These polos are designed with both style and functionality in mind, ensuring they look good and perform well under the summer sun. These statement prints add a playful yet sophisticated element to the garments, making them stand out on the course.</p><h5><strong>ACTIVE APPAREL</strong></h5><p>The active apparel in this collection is a highlight, featuring shorts, trousers, hoodies and mid-layers that cater to the demands of summer sports. Some pieces are rendered in solid hues, providing a classic and timeless look, while others boast geometric designs that add a modern and dynamic touch. </p><h5><strong>ACCESSORIES</strong></h5><p>No summer collection is complete without the right accessories, and J.Lindeberg has ensured that their Summer 2024 collection includes a range of stylish and practical options. Caps and socks are available to complement your outfit and provide additional comfort and protection from the elements. These accessories are designed to seamlessly integrate with the rest of the collection, enhancing your overall look and performance.</p>"
          }
        }
